# Inventory Management System

A REST API-based inventory management application built with Java, Spring Boot, and MySQL.

## Features

- Product management
- Inventory tracking
- CRUD operations
- REST APIs

## Tech Stack

- Java
- Spring Boot
- MySQL
- Maven

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/username/inventory-management.git
cd inventory-management
```

## Run

```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```

